# EDGE Glasses Firmware

ESP32 firmware for EDGE Smart LCD Glasses.

## Features

- BLE GATT server for wireless control
- Timed meditation sessions with breathing patterns
- Strobe frequency control (1-50 Hz)
- Hall sensor sleep/wake detection
- Power optimized (~29mA active, ~16ÂµA sleep)

## Hardware

- MCU: ESP32-PICO-D4
- PWM Output: GPIO27
- Hall Sensor: GPIO4
- BLE Service: 0x00FF

## Build

Requires ESP-IDF v5.x

\`\`\`bash
idf.py set-target esp32
idf.py build
idf.py -p /dev/ttyUSB0 flash monitor
\`\`\`

## BLE Protocol

See [API Reference](docs/API_REFERENCE.md) for complete command documentation.

### Quick Reference

| Bytes | Action |
|-------|--------|
| `[0x00-0xFF]` | Set opacity (single byte) |
| `[0xA1, start, end]` | Set strobe Hz range |
| `[0xA2, percent]` | Set brightness |
| `[0xA5, duty]` | Static hold |
| `[0xA6]` | Resume session |
| `[0xA7]` | Sleep |

